1. An inReach Satellite Communicator or comparale device
able to send text messages offshore to an email account and receive text messages from mobile phones.

2. a Google Mail account and the ability to use google script and google-spreadsheet.

3. a twilio.com account with a mobilephone number in order to be able to send an SMS to the inReach Satellite Communicator

4. Some technical and program skills to implement and modify the source code provided here.
